Package fr.ferret.model.state

Class State

java.lang.Object
fr.ferret.model.state.State
public final class State extends Object
An object representing the state of a processus (a download for example). It contains a text and a tooltip. It can be used to set the state of a state panel in the bottom panel, using the setState method.
